name: SelectionOptions

properties.name: ADD_TO
properties.description: Adds the object to the existing selection; if no object was previously selected, makes the object the only selected object.

properties.name: REPLACE_WITH
properties.description: Selects the object and deselects any previously selected objects.

properties.name: SET_KEY
properties.description: Sets the key object. At least 2 objects must be selected, and the key object specified must be one of them.

description: Options for selection status in relation to previously selected objects.
